{"tid":21982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔性盡現] 普巴：之前投祖記當度假","createTime":"2016-12-04T07:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T23:57:52.000Z","uid":14812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aab224894bd309450f5f5d73504dbfc8155f2094","tid":21982,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=cce444e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】出身曼聯的保羅普巴坦言，自己過往一直心繫曼聯，之前轉會祖雲達斯就只當是享受了一個愉快的假期。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯紅褲子出身的保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）2012年為了得到更多一隊上陣機會，毅然轉投祖雲達斯尋求更佳發展，4年過後，普巴在祖記踢出名堂，更以天價回流紅魔，即使離開過，但據該名法國中場指之前身在祖記，仍心繫曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n普巴對英國《天空體育》說：「我的心是靠向曼聯，那是我的家，當我離開時，我一直知道自己將會回歸，對我而言，那只是很正常的事，就好像出外度假，現在剛剛回來，認真地說，沒有東西真正改變，我仍然是同一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n普巴今季強勢回歸曼聯令紅魔粉絲滿有憧憬，但迄今予感覺是不足以協助曼聯再復班霸本色，更有人認為其表現跟身價並不相稱。回歸後，他至今為紅魔在所有賽事上陣過18次攻入4球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp16713482683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp16713482683&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6940ac71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp16713482683&h=577d26b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp16713482683</a>"},{"pid":"f53b875f405ef7d4d60165346998efb7fe862a82","tid":21982,"uid":10038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辣殺"},{"pid":"d1d20b94b0477fac650c7cbae8bcf16930e70425","tid":21982,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辣殺</blockquote><br />\n祖記的確係 配唔起我地普巴"},{"pid":"d6a9060d741d0076bbd14041177ad9886dc5c935","tid":21982,"uid":2358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"回歸後，他至今為紅魔在所有賽事上陣過18次攻入4球。"},{"pid":"2cea760d56d4e5b7c0486b87427f4f2dfe29af5d","tid":21982,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"🤗"},{"pid":"be32d996ea918ee8b4ebfa76312da526e7d6d8f8","tid":21982,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"而家似度緊假多d喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a40b371a69f806094d4b2d4b62a11f6c8f39c85","tid":21982,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"爽呀！"},{"pid":"3b00577f08ded095a19875c03554c2b053c6561a","tid":21982,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"返去度假啦垃圾"},{"pid":"2f97dff56a0cce136c7bfdade70ce9ffdb44e699","tid":21982,"uid":52754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返去度假啦垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩留<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9e49349e1fea1f79acfc0e6f31c6e9760dc9b","tid":21982,"uid":10303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"倒返轉下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f7c48c2d4ff8162f208f2bbff675762f56a7a6","tid":21982,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"家下當退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde711813fff309548e2a5155c9dfe80949c398f","tid":219